app-misc/homeassistant:tesla-wall-connector - The Tesla Wall Connector integration allows you to integrate your Gen 3 Tesla Wall Connector with Wi-Fi into Home Assistant.
app-misc/homeassistant:teslemetry - The Teslemetry integration exposes various commands and sensors from the Tesla vehicles and energy sites connected to a Teslemetry subscription.
app-misc/homeassistant:tessie - The Tessie integration exposes various commands and sensors from the Tesla vehicles and energy products connected to your Tessie subscription.
app-misc/homeassistant:thermobeacon - Integrates ThermoBeacon devices into Home Assistant.
app-misc/homeassistant:thermopro - Integrates ThermoPro devices into Home Assistant.
app-misc/homeassistant:thethingsnetwork - The The Things Network integration allows you to interact with the The Things Network from within Home Assistant. This community-driven and open network supports LoRaWAN for long-range (~5 to 15 km) communication with low bandwidth (51 bytes/message). Gateways transfer the received data from the sensors to The Things Network.
app-misc/homeassistant:thingspeak - The ThingSpeak integration makes Home Assistant communicate with the ThingSpeak API.For now, it records exactly one entity at once, which is great for testing purposes. For long-time storage you should rely on the InfluxDB integration.
