app-misc/homeassistant:victron-ble - The Victron BLE integration integrates Victron Energy devices that support the BLE protocol into Home Assistant.
app-misc/homeassistant:victron-remote-monitoring - The Victron Remote Monitoring (VRM) integration pulls site statistics, solar production and consumption forecasts from Victron Energy’s VRM portal into Home Assistant. It provides day-ahead, next-hour, and six-day outlooks for both production and consumption. It also includes peak-time predictions. The integration requires at least 30 days of VRM history before forecasts become available.
app-misc/homeassistant:vilfo - The Vilfo Router integration allows you to observe the state of your Vilfo Router from Home Assistant.
app-misc/homeassistant:vivotek - The VIVOTEK integration allows you to integrate a VIVOTEK IP camera into Home Assistant.
app-misc/homeassistant:vizio - The VIZIO SmartCast integration allows you to control SmartCast-compatible TVs and sound bars (2016+ models).
app-misc/homeassistant:vlc - The VLC media player integration allows you to control VLC media player.
app-misc/homeassistant:vlc-telnet - The VLC media player via Telnet integration allows you to control a VLC media player using the built in telnet interface.
app-misc/homeassistant:vodafone-station - The Vodafone Station integration allows you to control your Vodafone Station based router.
app-misc/homeassistant:voip - The VoIP integration enables users to talk to Assist using an analog phone and a VoIP adapter. Currently, the system works with the Grandstream HT801. See the tutorial for detailed instructions.
app-misc/homeassistant:volkszaehler - The Volkszaehler integration is consuming the system information provided by the Volkszaehler API.
app-misc/homeassistant:volumio - The Volumio integration allows you to control a Volumio media player from Home Assistant.
app-misc/homeassistant:volvo - The Volvo integration is used to integrate your Volvo vehicle.
